                    "parameterType": "ComponentParameter",
                    "usage": "NoPort"
                },
                {
                    "name": "func_code",
                    "value": "import dill\ndef first_line(filename):\n\tfilename = str(dill.loads(filename))\n\twith open(filename, \"r\") as f:\n\t\tline = f.readline()\n\tprint(f\"First line: {line}\")\n\treturn line\n",
                    "defaultValue": "",
                    "description": "Python function code, e.g. 'def func_name(args): return args'. Note that func_name above needs to match the defined name here.",
